snippet.title: Janet DeMornay is a Slumlord (and a Witch) - Official Trailer | The Indie Horror Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Live the anxieties and horrors of what it is to be a renter in a world run by landlords. …and your landlord is a witch. Coming to Steam in 2024.
